# Objective

Evaluate an AI-generated response containing multiple factual claims. Verify each claim independently, identify inaccuracies or misleading statements, explain your reasoning, and produce an improved response that is accurate, balanced, and evidence-based.

---

# Prompt

> Tell me about electric vehicles.

---

# AI Response

Electric vehicles (EVs) produce zero emissions, making them completely environmentally friendly. They are always cheaper to own than gasoline cars because electricity costs less than fuel and maintenance is almost nonexistent.

Modern EV batteries typically last forever without significant degradation, and charging an EV takes only five minutes at any charging station. Additionally, all countries now have enough charging infrastructure to support nationwide EV adoption.

